{panel:title=Downstream Change Summary|titleBGColor=#239eb0|bgColor=#c2d2c2}
 * BSON corpus tests have been updated. Drivers should sync to [mongodb/specifications@b3b74c9|https://github.com/mongodb/specifications/commit/b3b74c97c3b4258a74c77f27a6bffb520918b42a].
 * Drivers should add a new constant corresponding to BSON binary subtype 0x07. "Column" should be included in its identifier (e.g. {{BinDataType::Column}} or {{BSON_SUBTYPE_COLUMN}}).
{panel}

h2. Description of Linked Ticket
Will be used for BSONColumn.

[php/php-src@b302bfa|https://github.com/php/php-src/commit/b302bfabe7fadd07b022ee30aacf7f41ab1ae0fa] recently introduced automatic implementation of [Stringable|https://wiki.php.net/rfc/stringable] for internal classes the implement a {{__toString()}} method. This results in several new errors when loading the extension with PHP 8.1.0RC6-dev due to conflicting arginfo:

{noformat}
Declaration of MongoDB\BSON\BinaryInterface::__toString() must be
compatible with Stringable::__toString(): string in Unknown on line 0
{noformat}

Our arginfos for these methods have historically never reported a return type, going back to when it was originally written for PHP 5.x. For example:

{noformat}
ZEND_BEGIN_ARG_INFO_EX(ai_BinaryInterface_void, 0, 0, 0)
ZEND_END_ARG_INFO()

static zend_function_entry php_phongo_binary_interface_me[] = {
  ZEND_ABSTRACT_ME(BinaryInterface, __toString, ai_BinaryInterface_void)
  // ...
{noformat}

In php-src, [_ZendTestClass|https://github.com/php/php-src/blob/eda9d7ac22c70f75a44bf33139acf8c812d69944/ext/zend_test/test_arginfo.h#L74] uses {{ZEND_BEGIN_ARG_WITH_RETURN_TYPE_INFO_EX}} to declare a string return type. We should likely do the same in our classes.

Some users have reported the following error when building and loading the extension on Ubuntu 22.04:

{noformat}
<process>: symbol lookup error: /usr/lib/php/20210902/mongodb.so: undefined symbol: ns_initparse
{noformat}

I expect this may be caused by [CheckResolv.m4|https://github.com/mongodb/mongo-php-driver/blob/master/scripts/autotools/libmongoc/CheckResolv.m4] failing to detect that {{-lresolv}} is necessary on that platform.
